{"id":3550,"date":"2018-05-18T21:08:29","date_gmt":"2018-05-18T19:08:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/?p=3550"},"modified":"2018-05-18T21:08:29","modified_gmt":"2018-05-18T19:08:29","slug":"muffins-mirtilos-no-forno","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/2018\/05\/18\/muffins-mirtilos-no-forno\/","title":{"rendered":"Muffins &#038; Mirtilos no forno"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Deixei nas <em>m\u00e3os<\/em> de uma <em>pessoa<\/em> muito importante a escolha do ingrediente protagonista de alguns dos meus pr\u00f3ximos <em>posts<\/em>. N\u00e3o sei se lhe chame projecto, se lhe chame desafio. Na verdade, acho que \u00e9 apenas uma desculpa para passar mais tempo na cozinha&#8230;<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/IMG_20180518_175141-e1526668916725.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-3556\" src=\"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/IMG_20180518_175141-595x446.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"595\" height=\"446\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">O que me propuseram para esta semana n\u00e3o me pareceu nada dif\u00edcil. Ali\u00e1s, quando soube que o primeiro ingrediente ia ser o mirtilo, s\u00f3 uma receita me passou pela cabe\u00e7a &#8211; e fui a correr ver se tinha pelo menos 200gr no frigor\u00edfico para a fazer de imediato.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Muffins de mirtillo com cobertura crocante &#8211; h\u00e1 l\u00e1 melhor ideia para um lanche?<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fiz o primeiro tabuleiro na 3a feira e o segundo tabuleiro dois dias depois. Quantos muffins sobraram? &#8230;h\u00e1 por ali um, que n\u00e3o chega a ver a madrugada de S\u00e1bado.<\/p>\n<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-3550 gallery-columns-2 gallery-size-thumbnail'><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/fornada-1-e1526651743564.jpg'><img width=\"480\" height=\"640\" src=\"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/fornada-1-480x640.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-3518\" \/><\/a>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<figcaption class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-3518'>\n\t\t\t\tdav\n\t\t\t\t<\/figcaption><\/figure><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/fornada-2-e1526651833785.jpg'><img width=\"480\" height=\"640\" src=\"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/fornada-2-480x640.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-3520\" \/><\/a>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<figcaption class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-3520'>\n\t\t\t\tdav\n\t\t\t\t<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n<blockquote><p>Muffins de Mirtilo<\/p>\n<p>c\/ cobertura crocante<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p><strong><em>Ingredientes para a cobertura crocante:<\/em><\/strong><br \/>\n<em> 120gr de farinha<\/em><br \/>\n<em> 120gr de a\u00e7\u00facar<\/em><br \/>\n<em> 120gr de manteiga fria aos cubos<\/em><br \/>\n<em> 1 pitada de canela<\/em><br \/>\n<em> 1 pitada de sal fino<br \/>\n<\/em><\/p>\n<p><strong>Modo de prepara\u00e7\u00e3o:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pr\u00e9-aque\u00e7a o forno nos 180\u00b0.<br \/>\nColoque todos os ingredientes secos numa ta\u00e7a. Junte a manteiga bem fria, cortada aos cubos, e envolva com os dedos at\u00e9 que todos os ingredientes se integrem e fique com uma esp\u00e9cie de areia grossa.<\/p>\n<p>Se preferir, utilize o processador para preparar a cobertura.<\/p>\n<p><em><strong>Ingredientes para a massa<\/strong><\/em><br \/>\n<em>200gr de farinha<\/em><br \/>\n<em> 125gr de a\u00e7\u00facar<\/em><br \/>\n<em> 1 c. de ch\u00e1 bem cheia de fermento em p\u00f3<\/em><br \/>\n<em> 1 pitada de sal<\/em><br \/>\n<em> 1 pitada de canela<\/em><br \/>\n<em> 1 c. de caf\u00e9 de baunilha em p\u00f3<\/em><br \/>\n<em> 1 lim\u00e3o (raspa)<\/em><br \/>\n<em> 60ml de \u00f3leo<\/em><br \/>\n<em> 80ml de leite<\/em><br \/>\n<em> 1 ovo L<\/em><br \/>\n200gr de mirtilos<\/p>\n<p><strong>Modo de prepara\u00e7\u00e3o:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Junte todos os ingredientes secos numa ta\u00e7a e misture bem. Noutra ta\u00e7a, junte todos os ingredientes l\u00edquidos e a raspa de 1 lim\u00e3o.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Junte a mistura l\u00edquida \u00e0 ta\u00e7a dos ingredientes secos e envolva bem, at\u00e9 formar uma massa homog\u00e9nea e espessa. Adicione os mirtilos e mexa mais uma vez, com cuidado para n\u00e3o desfazer os mirtilos.<\/p>\n<div id='gallery-2' class='gallery galleryid-3550 gallery-columns-2 gallery-size-thumbnail'><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/2-ta\u00e7as-e1526651295433.jpg'><img width=\"480\" height=\"640\" src=\"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/2-ta\u00e7as-480x640.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" \/><\/a>\n\t\t\t<\/div><\/figure><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/mistura-final-e1526651901362.jpg'><img width=\"480\" height=\"640\" src=\"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/mistura-final-480x640.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" \/><\/a>\n\t\t\t<\/div><\/figure>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Deite 1 a 2 colheres de massa nas formas de papel (ocupando cerca de 3\/4 da forma). Deixe espa\u00e7o para uma boa quantidade de cobertura (que dever\u00e1 conservar no frio at\u00e9 \u00e0 hora de colocar nas formas).<\/p>\n<div id='gallery-3' class='gallery galleryid-3550 gallery-columns-2 gallery-size-thumbnail'><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/a-ir-ao-forno-e1526651363873.jpg'><img width=\"480\" height=\"640\" src=\"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/a-ir-ao-forno-480x640.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-3-3513\" \/><\/a>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<figcaption class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-3-3513'>\n\t\t\t\tdav\n\t\t\t\t<\/figcaption><\/figure><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/fornada-2-2-e1526651785706.jpg'><img width=\"480\" height=\"640\" src=\"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/fornada-2-2-480x640.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" \/><\/a>\n\t\t\t<\/div><\/figure>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Leve ao forno durante cerca de 20 minutos, fazendo depois o teste do palito para confirmar se os muffins est\u00e3o bem cozidos.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dificil? Demorado? Nada disso.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/o-muffin-e1526651964457.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-3522\" src=\"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/o-muffin-595x446.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"595\" height=\"446\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Digo-vos mais: melhor do que ir ao <em>Starbucks<\/em> comer um muffin de mirtilos, \u00e9 ir ao <em>Starbucks<\/em> e levar muffins de mirtilos de casa. N\u00e3o acreditam? Quem o fez que se acuse, por favor.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/os-muffins-e1526652050708.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-3524\" src=\"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/os-muffins-595x446.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"595\" height=\"446\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/alice-muffin-e1526651534123.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-3515\" src=\"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/alice-muffin-595x446.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"595\" height=\"446\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Mais uma vez, obrigada por continuarem por aqui comigo.<\/p>\n<p>At\u00e9 breve!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<div class=\"entry-summary\">\nDeixei nas m\u00e3os de uma pessoa muito importante a escolha do ingrediente&hellip;\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"link-more\"><a href=\"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/2018\/05\/18\/muffins-mirtilos-no-forno\/\" class=\"more-link\">Continue reading<span class=\"screen-reader-text\"> &ldquo;Muffins &#038; Mirtilos no forno&rdquo;<\/span>&hellip;<\/a><\/div>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":3523,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[63],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3550"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3550"}],"version-history":[{"count":9,"href":"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3550\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3562,"href":"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3550\/revisions\/3562"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/momscooking.ch\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3523"}],"wp:attachment":[{"hr